=Episode 15=

00:00:57.133 --> 00:00:57.733
Lan Mengyan,

00:00:58.932 --> 00:00:59.693
congratulations.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:01.390
Your long-held wish has come true.

00:01:21.253 --> 00:01:23.053
The Liu family has fallen.
The outcome's set.

00:01:23.670 --> 00:01:24.773
You should be celebrating.

00:01:26.493 --> 00:01:27.572
Why the long face?

00:01:33.053 --> 00:01:34.773
Killing them would've been easy,

00:01:35.613 --> 00:01:37.452
but I never wanted their lives.

00:01:38.973 --> 00:01:40.812
I wanted them to choke

00:01:42.932 --> 00:01:44.572
on the suffering they sowed.

00:01:46.493 --> 00:01:47.572
But Huanxi,

00:01:49.973 --> 00:01:50.852
Miss Lan,

00:01:51.773 --> 00:01:52.893
my family,

00:01:54.652 --> 00:01:55.812
all of them

00:02:00.372 --> 00:02:01.613
are gone for good.

00:02:29.460 --> 00:02:31.573
All I can hope is that
when the truth comes to light,

00:02:36.293 --> 00:02:37.812
it brings them

00:02:40.333 --> 00:02:41.773
some peace.

00:02:47.252 --> 00:02:48.053
Stop drinking.

00:03:20.173 --> 00:03:21.092
Go on…

00:03:30.252 --> 00:03:32.532
I'll keep digging into the powers
behind the Liu family.

00:03:33.173 --> 00:03:35.972
I won't stop…

00:03:38.212 --> 00:03:39.972
until I get to the bottom of it…

00:04:19.252 --> 00:04:20.690
From the items in the shop just now,

00:04:20.932 --> 00:04:21.890
aside from these three,

00:04:22.372 --> 00:04:24.012
pack the rest and send them

00:04:24.653 --> 00:04:27.053
to Miss Zhu's residence
on Zhuque Street.

00:04:28.093 --> 00:04:28.493
Yes,

00:04:29.012 --> 00:04:29.452
Madam.

00:04:37.250 --> 00:04:38.653
Madam, something terrible happened.

00:04:39.100 --> 00:04:39.692
It's bad news.

00:04:49.093 --> 00:04:49.572
Zhu!

00:04:58.692 --> 00:04:59.173
Zhu!

00:05:01.692 --> 00:05:02.413
Zhu!

00:05:04.252 --> 00:05:04.790
Look at this.

00:05:08.500 --> 00:05:08.912
(Zhu)

00:05:08.932 --> 00:05:10.132
(By the grace of your mercy,)

00:05:11.252 --> 00:05:12.213
(this wretched body)

00:05:12.892 --> 00:05:14.372
(caught a glimpse of life's warmth.)

00:05:16.012 --> 00:05:17.173
(But as a woman,)

00:05:17.853 --> 00:05:19.733
(I shouldn't have indulged in pleasure.)

00:05:21.200 --> 00:05:22.870
(Alas, I wasn't meant for such blessings.)

00:05:23.932 --> 00:05:25.590
(For that, I must repay them
with my life)

00:05:26.132 --> 00:05:27.372
(to find peace.)

00:05:50.493 --> 00:05:52.772
I won't allow anyone to tarnish

00:05:53.053 --> 00:05:54.772
the Liu family's good name!

00:06:27.653 --> 00:06:28.812
Did you find anything?

00:06:30.493 --> 00:06:31.390
Just as you suspected,

00:06:32.613 --> 00:06:33.332
Miss Zhu

00:06:34.093 --> 00:06:35.533
was from the Jade Spy Bureau.

00:06:41.293 --> 00:06:42.653
The Jade Spy Bureau?

00:06:44.053 --> 00:06:45.653
The same bureau

00:06:46.230 --> 00:06:48.810
that tormented us for three years
under the guise of discipline.

00:07:02.252 --> 00:07:03.653
You did well.

00:07:07.213 --> 00:07:09.493
Have the ledgers been put back?

00:07:10.350 --> 00:07:11.173
Rest assured, Master.

00:07:11.493 --> 00:07:13.053
I handled it myself.

00:07:13.613 --> 00:07:14.332
And those

00:07:14.613 --> 00:07:15.572
chests of jewels.

00:07:16.252 --> 00:07:18.053
Deliver them to the intended recipient.

00:07:18.400 --> 00:07:20.653
The money messenger's arrived
and waiting at the theater.

00:07:21.973 --> 00:07:23.533
(Chen Huanfeng must know something.)

00:07:27.973 --> 00:07:29.173
What do you need from me?

00:07:29.733 --> 00:07:30.613
Help me stage a scene.

00:07:31.533 --> 00:07:33.093
We'll draw Chen Huanfeng's attention.

00:07:39.452 --> 00:07:40.932
I can't live like this!

00:07:40.932 --> 00:07:41.733
Are you mad?

00:07:42.012 --> 00:07:44.012
Spouting such nonsense
in broad daylight!

00:07:45.613 --> 00:07:46.613
If I don't step outside,

00:07:46.772 --> 00:07:49.332
people will think he cast me aside!

00:07:49.572 --> 00:07:50.173
Madam,

00:07:50.452 --> 00:07:52.132
how can you talk so recklessly?

00:07:52.293 --> 00:07:54.012
You are airing your grievances in public.

00:07:54.012 --> 00:07:55.213
This is inappropriate conduct.

00:07:56.510 --> 00:07:57.910
Do you not care for your reputation?

00:07:58.173 --> 00:08:01.533
A proper woman minds
her virtue and her home.

00:08:01.853 --> 00:08:03.853
I… I'm ashamed on your behalf!

00:08:03.973 --> 00:08:04.572
Enough!

00:08:04.932 --> 00:08:06.973
Am I not even allowed to speak my pain?

00:08:07.053 --> 00:08:07.613
Madam Liu,

00:08:07.733 --> 00:08:09.173
I can't bear to watch you throw away

00:08:09.173 --> 00:08:10.372
your virtue and dignity.

00:08:10.372 --> 00:08:11.452
Do as you will.

00:08:11.692 --> 00:08:12.173
My Lord!

00:08:12.653 --> 00:08:13.572
Let me go!

00:08:13.572 --> 00:08:14.132
My Lord!

00:08:14.150 --> 00:08:15.293
- Don't leave!
- Stop pulling me!

00:08:15.293 --> 00:08:16.973
- Don't leave!
- Let go of me!

00:08:17.053 --> 00:08:18.892
- My Lord, don't go!
- Let me go!

00:08:19.533 --> 00:08:21.853
My Lord…

00:08:22.413 --> 00:08:24.252
Don't go…

00:08:24.733 --> 00:08:26.892
My Lord…

00:08:26.892 --> 00:08:28.093
You mustn't do this. Get up!

00:08:28.093 --> 00:08:29.932
My Lord, please don't go!

00:08:29.932 --> 00:08:30.853
Let me go!

00:08:31.173 --> 00:08:32.853
My Lord!

00:08:32.853 --> 00:08:33.892
Let go of me!

00:08:33.892 --> 00:08:36.132
Don't make me leave, My Lord…

00:08:36.132 --> 00:08:36.613
We…

00:08:41.493 --> 00:08:43.172
We can't be together any longer!

00:08:43.172 --> 00:08:44.172
My Lord!

00:08:49.493 --> 00:08:51.493
Young Madam Liu,
as the head of the Liu Residence,

00:08:51.613 --> 00:08:52.652
you must uphold propriety.

00:08:52.700 --> 00:08:53.950
There's no need to cling to him.

00:08:54.853 --> 00:08:56.333
Young Madam, please reconsider.

00:08:58.652 --> 00:09:00.613
You don't know anything.

00:09:04.812 --> 00:09:07.537
(Zhenbai Pavilion)

00:09:14.853 --> 00:09:17.132
Heavens above…

00:09:17.853 --> 00:09:20.532
This grand, empty residence…

00:09:21.493 --> 00:09:24.613
What's left for me to live for?

00:09:24.853 --> 00:09:27.573
I don't want to live anymore…

00:09:29.690 --> 00:09:30.693
Young Madam, you mustn't!

00:09:31.000 --> 00:09:32.720
- I don't want to live anymore!
- Madam, you mustn't!

00:09:32.733 --> 00:09:34.470
Young Madam,
please don't do anything rash.

00:09:34.772 --> 00:09:35.813
- Let go…
- Young Madam,

00:09:35.892 --> 00:09:36.733
I know a way,

00:09:37.292 --> 00:09:40.652
something that'll ease the sorrow
you've nowhere to release.

00:09:41.573 --> 00:09:43.333
Please, sit and hear me out.

00:09:46.372 --> 00:09:47.052
A way?

00:09:47.772 --> 00:09:49.292
What way could you possibly have?

00:09:50.252 --> 00:09:52.573
Everything in this world
can be sought and solved,

00:09:53.573 --> 00:09:55.853
except the loneliness in one's heart.

00:09:57.052 --> 00:09:59.532
There's no medicine for that.

00:10:00.693 --> 00:10:01.172
Young Madam,

00:10:02.093 --> 00:10:03.733
there's a place in the capital

00:10:03.973 --> 00:10:05.093
known as the Jade Spy Bureau.

00:10:05.892 --> 00:10:07.333
They don't just teach etiquette,

00:10:07.853 --> 00:10:09.132
they help untangle the heart

00:10:09.250 --> 00:10:10.412
and loosen one's obsessions.

00:10:11.252 --> 00:10:12.613
If you go there to study,

00:10:13.132 --> 00:10:15.012
you can ease your grief

00:10:16.532 --> 00:10:18.573
and learn refined manners,

00:10:19.213 --> 00:10:21.573
become a proper lady.

00:10:23.412 --> 00:10:24.573
There's such a place?

00:10:25.213 --> 00:10:26.052
Absolutely.

00:10:27.772 --> 00:10:28.252
Then…

00:10:28.613 --> 00:10:29.933
Send someone to find out

00:10:30.412 --> 00:10:31.412
what it takes

00:10:31.470 --> 00:10:32.613
to enter the Jade Spy Bureau.

00:10:32.853 --> 00:10:33.613
If it works out,

00:10:34.012 --> 00:10:35.132
you'll be well rewarded.

00:10:36.652 --> 00:10:37.093
Understood.

00:10:38.613 --> 00:10:39.213
Wonderful.

00:10:40.052 --> 00:10:40.933
I won't die anymore.

00:10:42.613 --> 00:10:44.132
I'll dress up beautifully

00:10:44.733 --> 00:10:45.613
and go see Mo.

00:10:49.973 --> 00:10:50.973
Mo,

00:10:52.733 --> 00:10:54.652
we can still spend our lives together.

00:10:54.733 --> 00:10:55.532
Mo.

00:10:59.213 --> 00:11:00.490
Why are you still standing there?

00:11:00.772 --> 00:11:01.652
Go!

00:11:01.973 --> 00:11:02.493
Yes.

00:11:12.000 --> 00:11:13.680
The wound goes deeper on the left
than on the right.

00:11:13.693 --> 00:11:15.190
This is not a mark left
by a vertical pull of force.

00:11:15.613 --> 00:11:16.132
Zhu…

00:11:17.333 --> 00:11:19.292
Zhu was strangled and dragged.

00:11:28.412 --> 00:11:29.652
Left deep, right shallow.

00:11:37.973 --> 00:11:38.892
A left-handed killer.

00:11:43.532 --> 00:11:44.813
(The one who killed Zhu)

00:11:45.252 --> 00:11:46.213
(was you after all,)

00:11:47.052 --> 00:11:48.333
(Chen Huanfeng.)

00:11:51.933 --> 00:11:52.813
Rich,

00:11:53.453 --> 00:11:54.372
foolish,

00:11:56.132 --> 00:11:57.386
(Lady Lan acquired)
and willing to walk straight

00:11:57.410 --> 00:11:58.493
(the Liu Residence's fortune)
into the fire.

00:11:59.120 --> 00:11:59.972
(yet still harbors delusions of marrying)
She's the perfect

00:11:59.996 --> 00:12:00.721
(His Lordship to climb higher)
candidate.

00:12:01.532 --> 00:12:04.093
I'll send you a formal invitation

00:12:04.613 --> 00:12:06.012
to the Jade Spy Bureau

00:12:07.892 --> 00:12:09.973
for proper training.

00:12:10.812 --> 00:12:11.581
(Lady Lan acquired the Liu Residence's
fortune yet still)

